{
  "chapter": "060",
  "title": "三王世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "霍去病上疏",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>冒死再拜上疏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>：<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>过听，让臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>领兵戍守边境。本应专心于边塞之思虑，即便暴骸中野也无以报答，怎敢另议他事以干扰当事者。只因见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>忧劳，哀怜<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>以致忘我，减膳减<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">乐</span>，削减<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官员额。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>们靠天佑，已能穿衣趋拜，至今尚无封号和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span>官。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>谦让不怀私念，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>私下期望，不敢越职进言。臣私心如犬<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>之忠，冒死愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>诏令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>，趁盛<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夏</span>吉时确定<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>的封位。唯愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>明察。臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>冒死再拜上奏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">乙亥</span>日，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍光\">光（霍光）</span>代理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尚书令</span>之职在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>上奏。制曰：\"下交<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>。\""
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "群臣请议立王",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">戊申</span>朔，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">乙亥</span>日，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍光\">光（霍光）</span>代理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尚书令</span>、丞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：尚书丞非\">非（尚书丞非）</span>，下达<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>文书到，说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵充\">充（赵充）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行令</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李息\">息（李息）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子少傅</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">安（任安）</span>代行<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宗正</span>事务，冒死上言：<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>上疏说：'<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>过听，让臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>领兵戍守边境。本应专心于边塞之思虑，即便暴骸中野也无以报答，怎敢另议他事以干扰当事者。只因见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>忧劳，哀怜<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>以致忘我，减膳减<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">乐</span>，削减<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官员额。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>们靠天佑，已能穿衣趋拜，至今尚无封号和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span>官。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>谦让不怀私念，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>私下期望，不敢越职进言。臣私心如犬<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>之忠，冒死愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>诏令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>，趁盛<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夏</span>吉时确定<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>的封位。唯愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>明察。'制曰'下交<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>'。臣谨与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中二千石</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙贺\">贺（公孙贺）</span>等议：古代裂土立国，并建<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>以承天子，是用以尊<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>、重<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>的。如今臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>上疏，不忘其职，借以宣扬圣恩，说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>谦卑自贬以劳<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，考虑<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>还未有封号。臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>等应奉大义尽职守，愚昧而未及思考。当前正值盛<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夏</span>吉时，臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>等冒死请<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>。冒死请定所立国名。\""
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "帝下议列侯",
      "text": "制曰：\"我听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>封<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬姓</span>并列为诸侯，或为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">子</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">男</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">附庸</span>。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>说'支子不祭'。你们说并建<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>是为重<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>却未曾听闻。再说上天并非专为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>而生民。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>德薄，海内未和洽，却要让教化未成的人勉强做连城之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，那么股肱大臣又何以劝勉？改议以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>家养他们。\""
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "重议立王",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">丙子</span>日，奏<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>冒死言：臣谨与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">婴齐</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中二千石</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙贺\">贺（公孙贺）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谏大夫</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">安（任安）</span>等议论：臣等伏闻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>封<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬姓</span>并列，奉承<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>因祖考显达，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯禽</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>而立，都建国为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，互相辅佐。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>奉法，各尽其职，国统因此完备。窃以为并建<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>所以重<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>，是因四海<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>各以其职奉贡祭祀。支子不能奉祭宗祖，这是<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">封建</span>使他们守藩国，是帝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>扶德施化之道。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>奉承天统，明开圣业，尊贤显功，兴灭继绝。续<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧文终</span>之后于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">酂</span>，褒奖<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平津侯</span>等。彰显<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六亲</span>之序，明示天施之属，使<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">封君</span>能推私恩分<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子弟</span>户邑，赐号尊建<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百有馀</span>国。如今却让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，则尊卑相越，位次失序，不能垂统于<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">万世</span>。臣请立臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">丙子</span>日奏<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "帝又引康叔事",
      "text": "制曰：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>的亲属有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十</span>人而独他受尊，是因嘉奖他有德。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭天</span>受命郊祭，所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国有白<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牡</span>、骍<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">刚</span>的牺牲。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群公</span>不用纯色，这是贤与不肖的差别。'高山仰之，景行乡之'，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>很仰慕。所以抑制未成材者，封为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>即可。\""
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "群臣再请",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>戊寅日，奏<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>冒死言：臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>等与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>、吏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谏大夫</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：博士庆\">庆（博士庆）</span>等议：冒死奏请<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>。制曰：'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>的亲属有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十</span>人而独他受尊，是因嘉奖他有德。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭天</span>受命郊祭，所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国有白<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牡</span>、骍<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">刚</span>的牺牲。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群公</span>不用纯色，这是贤与不肖的差别。\"高山仰之，景行乡之\"，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>很仰慕。所以抑制未成材者，封为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>即可。'臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将行</span>等伏闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>亲属有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十</span>人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>继位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>辅<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>，其<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八人</span>都因祖考之尊建为大国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>年幼，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>在三<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>之位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯禽</span>据国于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，大概赐爵受命之时，都未到成人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康叔</span>后来抗拒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禄父</span>之难，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯禽</span>平<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">淮夷</span>之乱。昔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">五帝</span>异制，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>爵<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五等</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">春秋</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三等</span>，都是因时而序尊卑。高<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>拨乱反正，昭示至德，平定海内，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">封建</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，爵位<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二等</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>有的还在襁褓就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>，奉承<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，为<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">万世</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>则，不可更改。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>躬行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>，体现<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣德</span>，兼备文武。显慈孝之行，广<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤能</span>之路。内襃有德，外讨强暴。极临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北海</span>，西至<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">月氏</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西域</span>，举国尊奉。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舆械</span>的费用，不摊派于民众。倾御府之<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">藏</span>赏赐元<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎</span>，开禁<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">仓</span>赈济贫穷，减戍卒一<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">半</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">百蛮</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，无不向风，承教称心。远方殊俗，重译而来朝，恩泽及于方外。因此珍兽到来，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">嘉穀</span>茂盛，天应显彰。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>支子封至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>，却让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>等窃伏思量，都认为尊卑失序，使<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>失望，不可。臣请立臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>、臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>。\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>癸未日，奏<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>，留中未下。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "再奏定议",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙贺\">贺（公孙贺）</span>、代行<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>事<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵充\">充（赵充）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子少傅</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">安（任安）</span>代行<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宗正</span>事务冒死言：臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>等前奏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">去病（霍去病）</span>上疏说，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>未有封号，臣谨与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中二千石</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谏大夫</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：博士庆\">庆（博士庆）</span>等冒死请<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>等为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>谦让文武，严于律己，及以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>未教化为辞。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>之议，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒者</span>称其术，或违其心。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>坚辞不许，要以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄青翟\">青翟（庄青翟）</span>等私下与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">寿成</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十七人</span>商议，都认为尊卑失序。高<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>创建<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太祖</span>，封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>，广支派辅佐。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>则不改，是为了宣扬至尊。臣请<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">史官</span>择吉日，具<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>仪上奏，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>奉上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舆地图</span>，其他都依前例办理。\"制曰：\"可。\""
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "卜吉立王",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>丙申日，奏<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙贺\">贺（公孙贺）</span>代行<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>事冒死言：<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵充\">充（赵充）</span>说占卜得<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八日</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">乙巳</span>日，可<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯王</span>。臣冒死奏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舆地图</span>，请定所立国名。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>仪另奏。臣冒死请示。\""
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "制曰立三王",
      "text": "制曰：\"<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广陵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。\""
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "诏令下达",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>丁酉日，奏<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>戊寅朔，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">癸卯</span>日，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>下达<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>下<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中二千石</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>下郡<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太守</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">诸侯相</span>，丞书从事下达当办之处。依律<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>办理。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "齐王册书",
      "text": "\"维<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">乙巳</span>日，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>在宗庙立子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。曰：於戏，小子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>，领受这青色的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社</span>土！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>承继祖考，按古制建尔封国，封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东土</span>，世代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝藩屏辅翼。於戏记住啊！恭顺<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>的诏令，天命不常。人之好德，能彰显光明。不图道义，会使<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>怠惰。尽心竭力，真诚执守中道，天禄永终。一旦有过错，便会对你的封国不利，也伤害你的身体。於戏，保国安民，岂能不敬慎！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>要引以为戒。\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "右齐王策",
      "text": "以上是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策</span>书。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "燕王册书",
      "text": "\"维<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">乙巳</span>日，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>在宗庙立子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。曰：於戏，小子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>，领受这黑色的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社</span>土！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>承继祖考，按古制建尔封国，封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北土</span>，世代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝藩屏辅翼。於戏！<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">荤粥氏</span>虐待老人怀禽兽心，侵犯寇盗，加以奸巧扰边萌。於戏！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将率</span>往征其罪，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">万夫长</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">千夫长</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十有二君</span>皆来，降旗而奔师。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荤粥</span>迁徙域外，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北州</span>得以安定。尽心竭力，勿生怨望，勿败德行，勿废武备。非训教之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>不得从征。於戏，保国安民，岂能不敬慎！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>要引以为戒。\""
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "右燕王策",
      "text": "以上是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策</span>书。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "广陵王册书",
      "text": "\"维<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">乙巳</span>日，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张汤\">汤（张汤）</span>在宗庙立子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广陵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。曰：於戏，小子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>，领受这红色的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社</span>土！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>承继祖考，按古制建尔封国，封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南土</span>，世代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝藩屏辅翼。古人有言说：'<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大江</span>之南，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">五湖</span>之间，其人轻浮。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杨州</span>保疆，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">要服</span>之地，不及以政教。'於戏！尽心竭力，战战兢兢，和顺民意，勿放纵嬉乐，勿近小人，谨守<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>则。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">书</span>说：'臣不作威，不作福，就没有后来的羞辱。'於戏，保国安民，岂能不敬慎！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>要引以为戒。\""
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "右广陵王策",
      "text": "以上是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广陵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策</span>书。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：古人有言\"爱之欲其富，亲之欲其贵\"。所以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>者裂土立国，封<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子弟</span>，是为了褒扬亲亲，排列骨肉，尊崇先祖，贵重支体，广同姓于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。这样形势坚强而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>室安定。自古至今，由来已久。没有什么不同，所以不另作论述。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的事情，无足采者。但封立三<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>谦让，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>守义，文辞灿然，很值得观赏，所以附入<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "褚先生自叙",
      "text": "褚先生说：臣有幸以文学做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍郎</span>，喜读<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>的列传。传中称三王世家文辞可观，求其世家始终未找到。我从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长老</span>好事者那里取其封<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策书</span>，排比其事而传之，令后世能观察<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤主</span>的意旨。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "武帝同日立三王",
      "text": "听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">孝武帝（汉武帝）</span>时，同日一同拜三个儿子为王：封一子于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，一子于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广陵</span>，一子于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。各根据儿子的才力智能、土地的刚柔、人民的轻重，为他们作<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策</span>以申诫。告王说：\"世代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝藩屏辅翼，保国治民，岂能不敬慎！王要引以为戒。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤主</span>所作，本非浅闻者所能懂，非博闻强记的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>也不能探究其意。至于其次序分绝，文字上下，简牍参差长短，都有寓意，人们未必能知。谨将真草<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">诏书</span>论次，编于左方。让读者自己通其意而解说。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "王夫人欲置雒阳",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫夫人</span>并受<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">武帝（汉武帝）</span>宠幸，生子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘闳\">闳（刘闳）</span>将立为王时，其母生病，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">武帝（汉武帝）</span>亲自去探问。问：\"儿子该做王了，你想让他封到哪里？\"王夫人说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>在，妾有何话可说。\"帝说：\"虽然如此，你想让他封在哪里？\"王夫人说：\"愿置于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>。\"武帝说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武库</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敖仓</span>，是天下险要之地，汉国的大都。自<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span>以来，没有儿子封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>的。除<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雒阳</span>外，其余皆可。\"王夫人不答。武帝说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关东</span>的封国没有大过齐的。齐东靠海，城郭广大，古时仅<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>城中就有十万户，天下膏腴之地没有比齐更盛的了。\"王夫人以手击头，谢道：\"幸甚。\"王夫人死后帝痛惜她，派使者授封说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>恭谨派遣使者太中大夫明送璧一块，赐夫人为齐王太后。\"子闳做齐王，年少，无子，立而不幸早死，国绝，为郡。天下称齐不宜为王之地。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "受土立社",
      "text": "所谓\"受此土\"，是说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span>始封者必受土于天子的社坛，归立为本国之社，按岁时祭祀。春秋大传说：\"天子之国有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰社</span>。东方青色，南方赤色，西方白色，北方黑色，上方黄色。\"所以将封在东方的取青土，封南方的取赤土，封西方的取白土，封北方的取黑土，封上方的取黄土。各取其色相应的土，用白茅包裹，筑成社坛。这是最初从天子受封者。这称为主土。主土，就是立社而奉之。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>承祖考\"，祖是先祖，考是父亲。\"维稽古\"，维是度、是念，稽是当，意为当顺古之道。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "戒齐王慎内",
      "text": "齐地多变诈，不习于礼义，所以告诫他说\"恭<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>之诏，唯命不可为常。人之好德，能明显光。不图于义，使君子怠慢。悉若心，信执其中，天禄长终。有过不善，乃凶于而国，而害于若身\"。齐王<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">回国</span>，左右以礼义维持，可惜中年早夭。然全身无过，符合策书之意。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "三王戒意",
      "text": "传说\"青取之于蓝，而青于蓝\"，这是教化使然。深远啊贤主，独见昭明：告诫齐王慎于内；告诫燕王勿生怨望，勿败德；告诫广陵王慎于外，勿作威福。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "戒广陵王",
      "text": "广陵在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">吴越</span>之地，其民精悍而轻浮，所以告诫说\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江湖</span>之间，其人轻浮。杨州保疆，三代之时，远而要使从中国风俗，不能大以政教治之，以意驭之而已。勿放纵嬉乐，勿近小人，谨守法度\"。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三江</span>、五湖有鱼盐之利，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铜山</span>之富，天下所仰。所以告诫说\"臣不作福\"，是说不让他行财币厚赏赐，以立声誉，为四方归顺。又说\"臣不作威\"，是说不让他因轻浮而违背大义。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "昭帝厚赏胥",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">孝武帝（汉武帝）</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">孝昭帝（汉昭帝）</span>初立，先〖○朝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广陵王胥</span>，厚赏赐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金钱</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">财币</span>，值<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千馀万</span>，增地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>，邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万户</span>。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "宣帝封胥四子",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">昭帝（汉昭帝）</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉宣帝\">宣帝（汉宣帝）</span>初立，感恩行义，在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">本始元年</span>中，裂<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>地，全部<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广陵王胥</span>的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四子</span>：一子为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">朝阳侯</span>；一子为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平曲侯</span>；一子为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">南利侯</span>；最爱的少子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘弘\">弘（刘弘）</span>，立为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高密王</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "胥谋反国除",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>果然作威作福，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚王延寿\">楚王（楚王延寿）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>往来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚王延寿\">楚王（楚王延寿）</span>扬言说：\"我先祖<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚元王\">元王（楚元王）</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高祖\">高帝（汉高祖）</span>的小弟，封<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十二城</span>。如今地邑越来越少，我想和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">广陵王（刘胥）</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">起兵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">广陵王（刘胥）</span>为皇上，我再王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十二城</span>，如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚元王\">元王（楚元王）</span>之时。\"事发觉后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>请求行<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">罚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>因骨肉之故，不忍对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>按法处置，下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">诏书</span>不治<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">广陵王（刘胥）</span>，只<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span>首恶<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚王延寿\">楚王（楚王延寿）</span>。传说\"<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">蓬</span>生<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">麻</span>中，不扶自直；白沙在泥中，与之皆黑\"，是说土地教化使之如此。后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胥\">胥（刘胥）</span>又祝诅谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "戒燕王守边",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地土瘠，北邻<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，其人民勇而少谋，所以告诫说\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荤粥氏</span>不孝而有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">禽兽</span>心，以盗窃侵犯边民。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">朕</span>诏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>往征其罪，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">万夫长</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">千夫长</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十有二君</span>皆来，降旗奔师。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荤粥</span>迁域远处，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北州</span>得以安定\"。\"尽心，勿生怨\"，是说不要从俗而生怨望。\"勿败德\"，是说不要违背德行。\"勿废备\"，是说不要缺乏武备，要常备<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。\"非教士不得从征\"，是说非习<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>者不得在左右。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "旦请入宿卫被斥",
      "text": "到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">武帝（汉武帝）</span>年高，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>不幸薨，未有所立，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>派使者上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>，请求亲身入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>宿卫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">孝武（汉武帝）</span>见其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>，掷地怒道：\"生儿应置于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>之乡，却置于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，果然有争心，不让之端已现。\"于是派使者立即在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阙</span>下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">斩</span>其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "昭帝即位旦生怨",
      "text": "及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">武帝（汉武帝）</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">昭帝（汉昭帝）</span>初立，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>果然作怨而望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>。自以为长子当立，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐王子刘泽</span>等谋反叛，放言说：\"我哪能有弟弟在呢！如今立的乃是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>的儿子。\"想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">起兵</span>。事发觉，当<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">昭帝（汉昭帝）</span>因亲情宽忍，压下不宣扬。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>请求，遣<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宗正</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公户满意</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，一起出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，风示他。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，各在不同日子，接见责备<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宗正</span>主管<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">诸刘</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">属籍</span>，先见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，一一陈说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">昭帝（汉昭帝）</span>实是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">武帝（汉武帝）</span>之子的情状。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍御史</span>又见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">正法</span>责之，问：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>欲<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">起兵</span>罪名明白，应当治罪。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>家有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">正法</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>犯纤介小罪过，即行法直断了，怎能宽容<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。\"以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文法</span>惊动他。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>气焰越低，心中恐惧。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公户满意</span>通晓<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">经术</span>，最后见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，引用古今通义、国家<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">大礼</span>，文章尔雅。对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>说：\"古代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>必内有异姓<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>，是用以端正骨肉；外有同姓<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>，是用以端正异族。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>辅<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span>其两弟，故天下治。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">武帝（汉武帝）</span>在时，尚能宽容<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">昭帝（汉昭帝）</span>初立，年幼，春秋正富，尚未亲政，委任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>。古代<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">罚</span>不阿护<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">亲戚</span>，故天下治。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>辅政，奉法直行，无敢阿私，恐不能宽容<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>可自谨，不要自令身死国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>，为天下笑。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕王旦</span>恐惧服罪，叩头谢过。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>欲和合骨肉，不忍以法伤之。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "旦再谋反自杀",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>又与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">左将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上官桀</span>等谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>，扬言说\"我排在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之次，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>不在，我应当立，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>共同抑制我\"等等。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍光\">光（霍光）</span>辅政，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>议说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕王旦</span>不改过悔正，行恶不变。\"于是脩法直断，行<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">罚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，如其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策</span>书所预示。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>请<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉昭帝\">孝昭（汉昭帝）</span>因骨肉之亲，不忍按法处置，宽◈<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘旦\">旦（刘旦）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。传说\"<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兰</span>根与<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">白芷</span>，浸在恶水中，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>不近，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>不服\"，说的就是浸染所致。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "宣帝复封燕",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉宣帝\">宣帝（汉宣帝）</span>初立，推恩宣德，在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">本始元年</span>中，全部恢复<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕王旦</span>的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两子</span>：一子为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安定侯</span>；立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>原<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广阳王</span>，以奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕王旦\">燕王（燕王旦）</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭祀</span>。"
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "三王封建，旧史灿然。 褚氏后补，册书犹存。 去病建议，青翟上言。 天子谦让，志在急贤。 太常具礼，请立齐燕； 闳国负海，旦社为玄。 宵人不近，荤粥远边。 明哉监戒，式防其愆。"
    }
  }
}